#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.104"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.104:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.104:0.2"
msgid "11. Valāhakavagga"
msgstr "11. Clouds"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.104:0.3"
msgid "104. Udakarahadasutta"
msgstr "104. Lakes"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.104:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārome, bhikkhave, udakarahadā."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these four lakes."

msgctxt "an4.104:1.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.104:1.3"
msgid ""
"Uttāno gambhīrobhāso, gambhīro uttānobhāso, uttāno uttānobhāso, gambhīro "
"gambhīrobhāso—"
msgstr ""
"~One is shallow but appears deep, ~one is deep but appears shallow, ~one is "
"shallow and appears shallow, and ~one is deep and appears deep."

msgctxt "an4.104:1.4"
msgid "ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro udakarahadā."
msgstr "These are the four lakes."

msgctxt "an4.104:1.5"
msgid ""
"Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, cattāro udakarahadūpamā puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā "
"lokasmiṃ."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, these four people similar to lakes are found in the world."

msgctxt "an4.104:1.6"
msgid "Katame cattāro?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.104:1.7"
msgid ""
"Uttāno gambhīrobhāso, gambhīro uttānobhāso, uttāno uttānobhāso, gambhīro "
"gambhīrobhāso."
msgstr ""
"~One is shallow but appears deep, ~one is deep but appears shallow, ~one is "
"shallow and appears shallow, and ~one is deep and appears deep."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.104:2.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo uttāno hoti gambhīrobhāso?"
msgstr "And how is a person shallow but appears deep?"

msgctxt "an4.104:2.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekaccassa puggalassa pāsādikaṃ hoti abhikkantaṃ paṭikkantaṃ "
"ālokitaṃ vilokitaṃ samiñjitaṃ pasāritaṃ saṅghāṭipattacīvaradhāraṇaṃ."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a person is impressive when going out and coming back, when "
"looking ahead and aside, when bending and extending the limbs, and when "
"bearing the outer robe, bowl and robes."

msgctxt "an4.104:2.3"
msgid ""
"So ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti … pe … ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī "
"paṭipadā’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti."
msgstr ""
"But they don’t really understand: ‘This is suffering’ … ‘This is the origin "
"of suffering’ … ‘This is the cessation of suffering’ … ‘This is the practice "
"that leads to the cessation of suffering’."

msgctxt "an4.104:2.4"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo uttāno hoti gambhīrobhāso."
msgstr "That’s how a person is shallow but appears deep."

msgctxt "an4.104:2.5"
msgid "Seyyathāpi so, bhikkhave, udakarahado uttāno gambhīrobhāso;"
msgstr "That person is like a lake that’s shallow but appears deep, I say."

msgctxt "an4.104:2.6"
msgid "tathūpamāhaṃ, bhikkhave, imaṃ puggalaṃ vadāmi."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.106"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an4.104:3.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo gambhīro hoti uttānobhāso?"
msgstr "And how is a person deep but appears shallow?"

msgctxt "an4.104:3.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekaccassa puggalassa na pāsādikaṃ hoti abhikkantaṃ "
"paṭikkantaṃ ālokitaṃ vilokitaṃ samiñjitaṃ pasāritaṃ "
"saṅghāṭipattacīvaradhāraṇaṃ."
msgstr "It’s when a person is not impressive …"

msgctxt "an4.104:3.3"
msgid ""
"So ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti … pe … ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī "
"paṭipadā’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti."
msgstr "But they really understand: ‘This is suffering’ …"

msgctxt "an4.104:3.4"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo gambhīro hoti uttānobhāso."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.104:3.5"
msgid "Seyyathāpi so, bhikkhave, udakarahado gambhīro uttānobhāso;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.104:3.6"
msgid "tathūpamāhaṃ, bhikkhave, imaṃ puggalaṃ vadāmi."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an4.104:4.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo uttāno hoti uttānobhāso?"
msgstr "And how is a person shallow and appears shallow?"

msgctxt "an4.104:4.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekaccassa puggalassa na pāsādikaṃ hoti abhikkantaṃ "
"paṭikkantaṃ ālokitaṃ vilokitaṃ samiñjitaṃ pasāritaṃ "
"saṅghāṭipattacīvaradhāraṇaṃ."
msgstr "It’s when a person is not impressive …"

msgctxt "an4.104:4.3"
msgid ""
"So ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti … pe … ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī "
"paṭipadā’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti."
msgstr "Nor do they really understand: ‘This is suffering’ …"

msgctxt "an4.104:4.4"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo uttāno hoti uttānobhāso."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.104:4.5"
msgid "Seyyathāpi so, bhikkhave, udakarahado uttāno uttānobhāso;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.104:4.6"
msgid "tathūpamāhaṃ, bhikkhave, imaṃ puggalaṃ vadāmi."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an4.104:5.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo gambhīro hoti gambhīrobhāso?"
msgstr "And how is a person deep and appears deep?"

msgctxt "an4.104:5.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekaccassa puggalassa pāsādikaṃ hoti abhikkantaṃ paṭikkantaṃ "
"ālokitaṃ vilokitaṃ samiñjitaṃ pasāritaṃ saṅghāṭipattacīvaradhāraṇaṃ."
msgstr "It’s when a person is impressive …"

msgctxt "an4.104:5.3"
msgid ""
"So ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti … pe … ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī "
"paṭipadā’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti."
msgstr "And they really understand: ‘This is suffering’ …"

msgctxt "an4.104:5.4"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo gambhīro hoti gambhīrobhāso."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.104:5.5"
msgid "Seyyathāpi so, bhikkhave, udakarahado gambhīro gambhīrobhāso;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.104:5.6"
msgid "tathūpamāhaṃ, bhikkhave, imaṃ puggalaṃ vadāmi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.104:5.7"
msgid ""
"Ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro udakarahadūpamā puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā "
"lokasmin”ti."
msgstr "These four people similar to lakes are found in the world.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.104:5.8"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
